;Mozilla Advocacy
Mozilla Advocacy {ok}


;Rallying citizens to protect the open Internet
Kimolojri'ïl winaqi' richin nikichajij ri jaqäl K'amaya'l


;Mozilla’s advocacy engine works with allies to cultivate a global force of tens of millions of people, who are aware of the issues that are vital to the future of the open Internet and prepared to take action in support of the rights of citizens of the web.
Ri ruk'u'x rutob'al Mozilla nisamäj kik'in achib'ilal richin ninuk' jun aj chijun kuchuq'a' kab'lajtäq chi t'ijtäq winaqi', ri yekich'öb' chi kij ri taq na'oj e k'atzinel chi re ruk'aslem ri jaqäl k'amaya'l ri chwa'q kab'ij chuqa' richin chi qanuk'un chik qi' toq xtiqatob'ej kich'ojib'al ruwinaq ajk'amaya'l.


;We are dedicated to building a world where:
Tajin yojsamäj chi runuk'ik jun ruwach'ulew akuchi':


;People are making more conscious choices to build and protect the open Internet
Ri winaqi' yekoqaj k'amonel taq na'oj richin nikinük' chuqa' nikichajij ri jaqäl K'amaya'l


;Companies and governments create products, policies and laws to support the open Internet because of public pressure to do so
Ri taq ajk'ayij moloj chuqa' taq chanpomanela' yekitz'ük taq tikojil, taq na'ojil chuqa' taqanem taq tzij richin nikito' ri jaqäl K'amaya'l ruma chi ri winaqi' nikich'ojij chi ke


;How we work: A focus on depth and scale
Achi'el yojsamäj: Jun rutzub'al rik'in panqaj chuqa' xakb'äl


;Mozilla’s advocacy approach incorporates both scale to depth and depth to scale to properly address the diversity of issues that we work on.
Ri rutzub'al Mozila richin nitalüx yerutz'aqatisaj ri xakb'äl pa panqaj achi'el chuqa' ri panqaj pa xakb'äl richin yesamajïx pa rub'eyal ri jalajöj rupam taq na'oj achoq pa ruwi' yojsamäj.


;This approach enables Mozilla to simultaneously build our capacity to mobilize millions of people quickly and grow our organizing power in local communities, which will make it possible to win on our issues in the long-term.
Re tzub'al re' nuya' q'ij chi re ri Mozilla nuk'iyirisaj junam ri qetamab'al richin aninäq yeqasiloj ri t'ijtäq chi winaqi' chuqa' richin niqajotob'a' ri quchuq'a' richin niqamöl qi' pa taq tinamït, ri xtuya' q'ij chi qe richin yeqaq'i' ri taq qataqikil pa taq juna' apo.


;We also push ourselves to be proactive — setting the topic and tone of the conversation, and promoting solutions — as well as reactive to current events or undesirable policies when necessary.
Chuqa' yojto'on richin yojsamäj — nijikib'äx ri taq ruk'u'x na'oj chuqa' ri rub'eyal ch'owen, chuqa' ri kitaluxik kisolik taq k'ayewal — achi'el chuqa' ri yekiyäk chik pe ri yek'ulwachitäj pe wakami o chuqa' ri itzilan taq na'ojil toq rajowaxik.


;Our initiatives
Tikirib'äl taq qasamaj


;Mozilla’s Advocacy Engine consists of five key initiatives:
Ri rusamajib'al Mozilla’s Advocacy rutzeqelb'en wo'o' ruk'u'x tikirib'äl taq samaj:


;Campaigns.
Taq samajinem.


;Our campaigns amplify the Mozilla community’s collective voice, in order to address the issues we believe must be tackled in the current era to build the open Internet we want. Example: <a href="%(url_encrypt_campaign)s">Encrypt</a>
Ri taq qasamajinem nikinimirisaj ri qach'ab'äl pa Mozilla tinamït, richin yeqasamajij ri taq ruk'u'x na'oj niqana'ojij chi k'atzinel yesamajïx wakami richin ninuk' ri jaqäl K'amaya'l niqarayib'ej. Achi'el: <a href="%(url_encrypt_campaign)s">Tewäx rusik'ixik</a>


;Online.
K'amab'ey.


;Naturally, the pulse of the movement to protect the open Internet lives on the web. We nurture a strong online community with a bias toward action, and drive mass digital mobilization behind our campaigns.
Kan k'o wi ri ruchuq'a' samaj richin nichajïx ri jaqäl K'amaya'l kan k'o wi pa ajk'amaya'l. Tiqatikirisaj jun nimaläj tinamït pa k'amab'ey rik'in rub'anik, chuqa' nuyäk jun nimaläj silonem na'ob'alil kitzeqelb'en ri taq qasamajinem.


;Media.
Q'ojom


;We tell creative, compelling stories that bring the biggest challenges and opportunities facing the open Internet to life, and into the mainstream.
Niqatzijoj chawe jeb'ël chuqa' jikïl taq b'anob'äl, ri yekicholajij ri nima'q taq jiq'ilib'em chuqa' taq ramajil achoq rik'in nujunamaj ri' ri jaqäl K'amaya'l pa ruk'aslem, chuqa' chupam ri nïm rub'ey.


;Field.
K'ojlem


;We connect, support and amplify the work of technologists, policy wonks, artists and activists committed to helping shape and drive Mozilla’s campaigns.
Yojximon, yojto'on chuqa' niqanimirisaj kisamaj ri ajna'ob'äl, ri yech'akon ri taq na'ojil, ri ajb'anonem chuqa' ri taq samajela' kiya'on kiq'a' richin yeto'on richin yekinük' chuqa' nikik'waj kib'ey ri taq rusamajinem Mozilla.


;Infrastructure and networks.
Ch'akulal chuqa' taq k'amab'ey.


;The foundation that supports and drives our advocacy work, by bringing together awesome people, organizations and technology to fuel our campaigns and the wider movement. Example: <a href="%(url_owf)s">Open Web Fellows</a>
Ri moloj nito'on chuqa' nuq'alajisaj ri qasamaj richin taluxïk, rik'in kimolik winaqi', taq moloj chuqa' jeb'ël taq na'ob'äl richin yeruk'iyirisaj pa nïm ri taq qasamajinem chuqa' taq silonem. Achi'el: <a href="%(url_owf)s">Open Web Fellows</a>


